****************** Library Fatal Error Codes ******************

File ERRORINF.$$$ has the format

SSSS:OOOO CCCC

***** IF SSSS:OOOO = ????:???? THEN ERROR IS FROM LOADER. *******

where S = code segment, O = IP value and C = Hex error code.

Run-time Checks:

01H  Stack overflow
02H  Null pointer de-reference
03H  Termination caused by signal.  (User break or Floating point exception)
04H  Overflow.
05H  Range.
06H  No Return.
07H  No matching Case Label.
08H  Long Integer Divide By Zero.
09H  Index Error.
0AH  Pure Virtual Function Called.

Misc Errors :

10H  Memory allocation initialisation (Out Of Memory)
11H  I/O initialisation (Out Of Memory)
12H  Invalid use of near heap in DLL.
13H  Complex Number Error.

21H  Dos Re-entered.
22H  NullProc Called.

Window module:

30H  Invalid window
31H  Use memory allocation
32H  Settitle memory allocation
33H  Initialisation error (Out Of Memory)

