37H  _wrint, Conversion Error.
38H  _wrchar, Illegal Parameter.
39H  _wrbool, Illegal Parameter.
3AH  _wrastr, Illegal Parameter.
3BH  _wrcstr, Illegal Parameter.
3CH  _wrreal, Illegal Parameter.
3DH  _wrreal, Conversion Error.
3EH  _f_wrint, Illegal Parameter.
3FH  _f_wrint, Conversion Error.

